~ -> tilda --->   home directory  cd ~/desktop
* star -> all -> rm *.tar *.zip
# hash - comment
$ dollar -> variables or to the last
^ cap  -> start
& ampersand  ->  backend process 
#! -> shebang  ->  magic character  -> defines the shell into which the script will run
#!/usr/bin/bash

\ -> escape character -> removes the value of wildcard
